---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Case Study: Bar Chantilly Carmagnola - Percorso Phygital | Bitora"
  description="Anteprima del case study Bar Chantilly: tessere NFC, loyalty digitale e nuove landing eventi per il locale storico di Carmagnola."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 via-white to-primary/20 dark:from-rose-950/30 dark:via-black dark:to-primary/20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Work in progress</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Bar Chantilly Carmagnola</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Un percorso phygital per raddoppiare gli eventi privati e creare relazioni durature con tessere NFC, loyalty digitale e comunicazione coordinata.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr,1.15fr] lg:items-center">
          <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-lg dark:bg-black/50">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Obiettivi condivisi</h2>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Digitalizzare menu e carte dessert con tessere NFC e QR dinamici.</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Creare landing dedicate per eventi privati con workflow approvazione rapido.</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Avviare loyalty program digitale e automazioni WhatsApp Business.</span></li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-primary">•</span><span>Preparare dataset strutturati per SEO locale e answer engine AI.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Percorso consulenziale</h2>
            <p>
              Insieme al team di Bar Chantilly abbiamo mappato i momenti chiave del servizio, dai clienti abituali ai gruppi che scelgono il locale per ricorrenze. Il lavoro prosegue in sprint bisettimanali con materiali condivisi su Notion e test in sala reale.
            </p>
            <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/10 p-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/80">Risultato atteso</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm">2× richieste eventi privati entro marzo 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/70 bg-white/80 p-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Stato</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Prototipi approvati, in corso implementazione fidelity card</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950/40">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Sprint di lavoro</h2>
          <div class="mt-8 space-y-5">
            {[ 
              {
                title: 'Audit & storytelling',
                description: 'Interviste con staff e clienti abituali, raccolta recensioni storiche, definizione tono di voce e palette visiva.'
              },
              {
                title: 'Esperienza NFC in sala',
                description: 'Progettazione menu digitali, test con tessere personalizzate, flussi dinamici per promuovere signature cocktail e dessert.'
              },
              {
                title: 'Loyalty & eventi',
                description: 'Landing eventi con automazioni WhatsApp, dashboard prenotazioni e programma punti per clienti ricorrenti.'
              }
            ].map((item, index) => (
              <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/70 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Sprint {index + 1}</span>
                  <span class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 text-xs font-semibold text-primary">Durata: 2 settimane</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">{item.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Aggiornamenti in arrivo</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Stiamo raccogliendo testimonial video e dati sulle prenotazioni eventi post-lancio. Il case study completo includerà dashboard interattive e kit grafici scaricabili.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
            <a href="/contattaci" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-custom-lg transition-colors hover:bg-primary-600">Prenota una consulenza</a>
            <a href="/lavori" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-primary/40 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10 dark:border-white/20 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-white/10">Torna al portfolio</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
